: 321, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"her gender\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"human dignity\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" athletes\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"the international backlash\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerian athlete spoke about her tumultuous Olympic experience on Sunday night in an interview with SNTV, a sports video partner of The Associated Press.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999967222410363, \"rank\": 1.6713008833551858e-06, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9641338983014683, \"rank\": 0.03720033261123239, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her tumultuous Olympic experience\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday night\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"SNTV\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports video partner\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I send a message to all the people of the world to uphold the Olympic principles and the Olympic Charter, to refrain from bullying all athletes, because this has effects, massive effects,\\\" Khelif said in Arabic.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic principles\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Charter\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"all athletes\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"effects\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"massive effects\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"Arabic\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It can destroy people, it can kill people's thoughts, spirit and mind.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"people's thoughts\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"spirit\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can divide people.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And because of that, I ask them to refrain from bullying.\\\"\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The victories of Khelif and fellow boxerLin Yu-tingof Taiwan in the ring in Paris have become one of the biggest stories of the 2024Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 3.931265192074248e-11, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.851015987104504e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The victories\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stories\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both women have clinched their first Olympic medals even as they have faced online abuse based on unsubstantiated claims about their gender, drawing them into a wider divide over changing attitudes toward gender identity and regulation in sports.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both women\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"their first Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"unsubstantiated claims\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"their gender\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider divide\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"attitudes\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"gender identity\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"regulation\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old Khelif acknowledged the pressure and pain of enduring this ordeal while competing far from home in the most important event of her athletic career.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 25-year-old Khelif\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"this ordeal\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"the most important event\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"her athletic career\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am in contact with my family two days a week, I hope that they were not affected deeply,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are worried about me.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"God willing, this crisis will culminate in a gold medal, and that would be the best response.\\\"\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this crisis\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"the best response\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vitriol stems from claims by the International Boxing Association, which has been permanently banned from theOlympics, that both Khelif and Lin failed unspecified eligibility tests for the women's competition at last year's world championships.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.914528259370798e-30, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vitriol\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"claims\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"both Khelif\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"unspecified eligibility tests\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's competition\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's world championships\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif declined to answer when asked whether she had undergone tests other than doping tests, saying she did not want to talk about it.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"undergone tests\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"doping tests\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She expressed gratitude to the International Olympic Committee and its president, Thomas Bach, for standing resolutely behind her while the banned former governing body of Olympic boxing stoked a furor around her participation in Paris.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2229, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 2428, \"end\": 2433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.851015987104504e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gratitude\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"its president\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"the banned former governing body\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic boxing\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"a furor\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"her participation\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions 10 great gift ideas that earn you Avios \\\"I know that the Olympic Committee has done me justice, and I am happy with this remedy because it shows the truth,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2567, \"end\": 2583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"10 great gift ideas\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"Avios\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Committee\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"this remedy\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"the truth\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also has seen massive support at her bouts, drawing cheers when she enters the arena and crowds waving Algerian flags chanting her first name.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2914, \"end\": 2922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999967222410363, \"rank\": 1.6713008833551858e-06, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"massive support\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"her bouts\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"cheers\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2895}, {\"ngram\": \"crowds\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"her first name\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will fight again on Tuesday in the women's 66kg semi-finals at Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 66kg\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3005}, {\"ngram\": \"semi\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland Garros\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif repeatedly made clear she will not allow chatter or accusations to deter her from attempting to claim Algeria's first Olympic gold medal in women's boxing.\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999994354044932, \"rank\": 4.948269395642149e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"chatter\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3092}, {\"ngram\": \"accusations\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"women's boxing\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not care about anyone's opinion,\\\" Khelif said a day afterbeating Anna Luca Hamori of Hungary.\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\", \"score\": 0.9443594635358885, \"rank\": 0.058918807166754544, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\"}, {\"begin\": 3292, \"end\": 3299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.6210478730328577, \"rank\": 0.6039999336511842, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone's opinion\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came here for a medal, and to compete for a medal.\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will certainly be competing to improve (and) be better, and God willing, I will improve, like every other athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"every other athlete\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although she is aware of the worldwide discussion about her, Khelif said she has been somewhat removed.\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worldwide discussion\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, I do not follow social media,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a mental health team that does not let us follow social media, especially in the Olympic Games, whether me or other athletes.\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mental health team\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3661}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3682}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3702}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3735}, {\"ngram\": \"whether me\", \"from\": 3737, \"to\": 3747}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am here to compete and get a good result.\\\"\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good result\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif started her Olympic run last Thursday with a victory over Angela Carini of Italy,who abandoned the bout after just 46 seconds.\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3878, \"end\": 3891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103664941, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 3895, \"end\": 3900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9894801824533345, \"rank\": 0.010602173727765068, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3819}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic run\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3843}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3872}, {\"ngram\": \"the bout\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"just 46 seconds\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini later said she regretted her decision and wished to apologize to Khelif.\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 4026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3947, \"end\": 3953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.7285102446893796, \"rank\": 0.3726642930418671, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 3991}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That unusual ending raised the chatter around Khelif into a roar, drawing comments from the likes of former U.S. President Donald Trump, \\\"Harry Potter\\\" writer J.K. Rowling and others falsely claiming Khelif was a man or transgender.\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4151, \"end\": 4163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999996275619, \"rank\": 3.725143615329303e-10, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 4166, \"end\": 4178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.862648560123923e-14, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}, {\"begin\": 4187, \"end\": 4191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7699732258815184e-35, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That unusual ending\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"the chatter\", \"from\": 4055, \"to\": 4066}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4080}, {\"ngram\": \"a roar\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4092}, {\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4110}, {\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 4116, \"to\": 4125}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4210}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4234}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 4239, \"to\": 4244}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender\", \"from\": 4248, \"to\": 4259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC repeatedly declared her and Lin qualified to participate in the Olympics, and it has decried the murky testing standards and untransparent governance of the IBA, which was banished entirely from the Olympics last year in an unprecedented punishment for a governing body.\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4266, \"end\": 4269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0618006572470416e-37, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4427, \"end\": 4430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999400974975, \"rank\": 5.990255033095094e-08, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4301}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4342}, {\"ngram\": \"the murky testing standards\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4390}, {\"ngram\": \"untransparent governance\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4419}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4465, \"to\": 4477}, {\"ngram\": \"an unprecedented punishment\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4518}, {\"ngram\": \"a governing body\", \"from\": 4523, \"to\": 4539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif clearly felt the weight of the worldwide scrutiny upon her, and her victory over Hamori on Saturday appeared to be cathartic.\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4572}, {\"ngram\": \"the worldwide scrutiny\", \"from\": 4576, \"to\": 4598}, {\"ngram\": \"her victory\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4624}, {\"ngram\": \"Hamori\", \"from\": 4630, \"to\": 4636}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 4640, \"to\": 4648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the referee raised Khelif's hand for the win, she went to the centre of the ring, waved to her fans, knelt and slammed her palm on the canvas, her smile turning to tears.\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the referee\", \"from\": 4681, \"to\": 4692}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's hand\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4713}, {\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4725}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4749}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4761}, {\"ngram\": \"her fans\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4780}, {\"ngram\": \"her palm\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4808}, {\"ngram\": \"the canvas\", \"from\": 4812, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"her smile\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4833}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not control my nerves,\\\" Khelif said in the interview.\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my nerves\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4883}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 4892}, {\"ngram\": \"the interview\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because after the media frenzy and after the victory, there was a mix of joy and at the same time, I was greatly affected, because honestly, it wasn't an easy thing to go through at all.\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 5103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the victory\", \"from\": 4958, \"to\": 4969}, {\"ngram\": \"a mix\", \"from\": 4981, \"to\": 4986}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 4990, \"to\": 4993}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 5001, \"to\": 5014}, {\"ngram\": \"an easy thing\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was something that harms human dignity.\\\"\", \"from\": 5104, \"to\": 5147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5111, \"to\": 5120}, {\"ngram\": \"human dignity\", \"from\": 5132, \"to\": 5145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had competed in IBA events for several years without problems until she was abruptly suspended from last year's world championships.\", \"from\": 5149, \"to\": 5285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5169, \"end\": 5172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999400974975, \"rank\": 5.990255033095094e-08, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several years\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5197}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 5206, \"to\": 5214}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's world championships\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Russian-dominated body - which has faced years of clashes with the IOC - has refused to provide any information about the tests.\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5357, \"end\": 5360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0618006572470416e-37, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Russian-dominated body\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5312}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 5331, \"to\": 5336}, {\"ngram\": \"clashes\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5347}, {\"ngram\": \"any information\", \"from\": 5386, \"to\": 5401}, {\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 5408, \"to\": 5417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Algeria's national boxing federation is still an IBA member.\", \"from\": 5419, \"to\": 5479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5419, \"end\": 5426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999994354044932, \"rank\": 4.948269395642149e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 5468, \"end\": 5471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999400974975, \"rank\": 5.990255033095094e-08, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif is from rural north-west Algeria, and she grew up playing football until she fell in love with boxing.\", \"from\": 5481, \"to\": 5590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5513, \"end\": 5520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999994354044932, \"rank\": 4.948269395642149e-07, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5481, \"to\": 5487}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 5546, \"to\": 5554}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 5573, \"to\": 5577}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 5583, \"to\": 5589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Overcoming her father's initial objections, she traveled 10km by bus to train for fights in a neighbouring town.\", \"from\": 5591, \"to\": 5703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her father's initial objections\", \"from\": 5602, \"to\": 5633}, {\"ngram\": \"bus\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5659}, {\"ngram\": \"fights\", \"from\": 5673, \"to\": 5679}, {\"ngram\": \"a neighbouring town\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After reaching the sport's top level in her late teens, she struggled early in her career before reaching an elite level.\", \"from\": 5705, \"to\": 5826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport's top level\", \"from\": 5720, \"to\": 5741}, {\"ngram\": \"her late teens\", \"from\": 5745, \"to\": 5759}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5794}, {\"ngram\": \"an elite level\", \"from\": 5811, \"to\": 5825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has been a solid, if unspectacular, international competitor for six years, and she lost to eventual gold medalist Kellie Harrington of Ireland at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 5827, \"to\": 6000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5949, \"end\": 5966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kellie Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 5970, \"end\": 5977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.7042928957694814, \"rank\": 0.3754972363613871, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5827, \"to\": 5833}, {\"ngram\": \"a solid, if unspectacular, international competitor\", \"from\": 5843, \"to\": 5894}, {\"ngram\": \"six years\", \"from\": 5899, \"to\": 5908}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 5981, \"to\": 5999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's next